Marking Scheme

  1. A+:Show good understanding of the course material; Homework is finished ON TIME and is performed in a way that beyond the requirements; Be willing to help on the forum.

 

  1. A:Show good understanding of the course material; Homework is finished and meets all requirements.

 

  1. B:Show good understanding of the course material; Homework is finished while some requirements is only partially met

 

  1. C:Show poor understanding of the course material; Homework is finished while some serious mistakes or malfunctions are observed in the homework.

 

  1. D:Homework are not finished

 

  1. O:No homework is found

 

Note:

  • In order to get an A+, make sure that you do not modify the homework after the deadline(Friday, 12 P.M.)
  • Homework should better be written in English. Chinese can be used in the final exam, but the paper based exam is printed in English.
